      "created_at": "2017-07-07T11:38:47.315Z",
      "cooked": "<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/5/554ec12aa87aa2cab41fb8db2f8507e6c86f7824.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/554ec12aa87aa2cab41fb8db2f8507e6c86f7824\" title=\"trump putin.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/5/554ec12aa87aa2cab41fb8db2f8507e6c86f7824.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"453\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/554ec12aa87aa2cab41fb8db2f8507e6c86f7824_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">trump putin.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1372×777 76.2 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p><em>Christopher Miller (ChristopherJM)/Twitter</em></p>\n<p>Këto janë fotot e para të postuara në Twitter të takimit të parë presidencial midis Presidentit Trump dhe Presidentit Putin në Hamburg. Ka patur një shtrëngim duarsh dhe një rrahje shpatullash, në përgjithësi gjuhë trupi shumë miqësore. Siç e dini,takimi vjen pas muajsh të tërë hetimesh në Shtetet e Bashkuara, ku agjencitë e inteligjencës janë të bindur se Rusia u përpoq të ndikonte rezultatin e zgjedhjeve amerikane, në favor të Trump. Trump nga ana e tij i qëndron bindjes se “askush nuk e di me të vërtetë. Mund të kenë qënë rusët, por fare mirë mund të kenë qënë të tjerë.”</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/9/9856dfe72d11364359d75bde6086630d541ea7e9.jpg\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/9856dfe72d11364359d75bde6086630d541ea7e9\" title=\"tp2.jpg\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/9/9856dfe72d11364359d75bde6086630d541ea7e9.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"449\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/9856dfe72d11364359d75bde6086630d541ea7e9_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">tp2.jpg</span><span class=\"informations\">1377×774 141 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<aside class=\"onebox twitterstatus\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ChristopherJM/status/883282825532895233\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">twitter.com</a>\n  </header>\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1104493055753764865/aED3ifHB_400x400.jpg\" class=\"thumbnail onebox-avatar\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\">\n<h4>\n  <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ChristopherJM/status/883282825532895233\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">\n    Christopher Miller (ChristopherJM)\n  </a>\n</h4>\n\n<div class=\"tweet\">THE HANDSHAKE. And a back pat. Trump and Putin meet at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23G20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">#G20</a>. via official German Govt Facebook page <a href=\"https://t.co/vYAsg0iyFi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://t.co/vYAsg0iyFi</a><div class=\"aspect-image-full-size\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:695/391;\"><img class=\"tweet-image\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DEIMqF1W0AECDQ9.jpg\"></div>\n<div class=\"aspect-image-full-size\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:695/389;\"><img class=\"tweet-image\" src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DEIMzuUXcAAL0wJ.jpg\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"date\">\n  <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ChristopherJM/status/883282825532895233\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">11:13 AM - 7 Jul 2017</a>\n    <span class=\"like\">\n      <svg viewbox=\"0 0 512 512\" width=\"14px\" height=\"16px\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <path d=\"M462.3 62.6C407.5 15.9 326 24.3 275.7 76.2L256 96.5l-19.7-20.3C186.1 24.3 104.5 15.9 49.7 62.6c-62.8 53.6-66.1 149.8-9.9 207.9l193.5 199.8c12.5 12.9 32.8 12.9 45.3 0l193.5-199.8c56.3-58.1 53-154.3-9.8-207.9z\"></path>\n      </svg> 86\n    </span>\n    <span class=\"retweet\">\n      <svg viewbox=\"0 0 640 512\" width=\"14px\" height=\"16px\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <path d=\"M629.657 343.598L528.971 444.284c-9.373 9.372-24.568 9.372-33.941 0L394.343 343.598c-9.373-9.373-9.373-24.569 0-33.941l10.823-10.823c9.562-9.562 25.133-9.34 34.419.492L480 342.118V160H292.451a24.005 24.005 0 0 1-16.971-7.029l-16-16C244.361 121.851 255.069 96 276.451 96H520c13.255 0 24 10.745 24 24v222.118l40.416-42.792c9.285-9.831 24.856-10.054 34.419-.492l10.823 10.823c9.372 9.372 9.372 24.569-.001 33.941zm-265.138 15.431A23.999 23.999 0 0 0 347.548 352H160V169.881l40.416 42.792c9.286 9.831 24.856 10.054 34.419.491l10.822-10.822c9.373-9.373 9.373-24.569 0-33.941L144.971 67.716c-9.373-9.373-24.569-9.373-33.941 0L10.343 168.402c-9.373 9.373-9.373 24.569 0 33.941l10.822 10.822c9.562 9.562 25.133 9.34 34.419-.491L96 169.881V392c0 13.255 10.745 24 24 24h243.549c21.382 0 32.09-25.851 16.971-40.971l-16.001-16z\"></path>\n      </svg> 120\n    </span>\n</div>\n\n  </article>\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
