    {
      "id": 41542,
      "post_number": 3,
      "username": "ACDC",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/e68b1a/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2017-07-07T11:54:54.699Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Ne fakt Rusia jo vetem qe ndihmoi Trumpin,por ndohmoi edhe Republikanet te mbajne fitoret ne senat dhe ne dhomen e perfaqesuesve.</p>\n<p>Pas kesaj ndihmoi republikanet te fitojne 1000 vende ne parlamentet shteterore,te fitoje 2/3 e guvernatoreve, se fundi edhe ne garen ne shtetin e Xhorxhias.<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/grinning.png?v=9\" title=\":grinning:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":grinning:\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/grinning.png?v=9\" title=\":grinning:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":grinning:\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/grinning.png?v=9\" title=\":grinning:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":grinning:\"></p>\n<p>Dje ne Varshave Trump u shpreh me qarte se kurre ndaj nderhyrjes se Rusise ne Ukrahine dhe ne mbrojtje te artikullit te 5-te te NATO-s.</p>\n<p>Se fundi,e majta “harron” qe Obama coi sekrataren Clinton ti kerkoje falje Rusise me butonin e famshem Start up.<br>\nCudi nga e majta kjo dhe takimet me Chaves,Kastron u pane si gjera te mira.</p>\n<p>Personalisht mendoj qe marredheniet SHBA-Rusi do te shkojne me keq edhe gjate presidences Trump.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/2/2d381a1bd60ca9ac413a86f7631f8b090aa48f13.JPG\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/2d381a1bd60ca9ac413a86f7631f8b090aa48f13\" title=\"IMG_0897.JPG\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/2/2d381a1bd60ca9ac413a86f7631f8b090aa48f13.JPG\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2d381a1bd60ca9ac413a86f7631f8b090aa48f13_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_0897.JPG</span><span class=\"informations\">1200×900 122 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "like_count": 0
